      • leadingComments

        public java.util.Optional<java.lang.String> leadingComments()
        Obtains the comments going before a rejection declaration.

        Requires the following Protobuf plugin configuration: 

         
 generateProtoTasks {
     all().each { final task ->
         // If true, the descriptor set will contain line number information
         // and comments. Default is false.
         task.descriptorSetOptions.includeSourceInfo = true
         // ...
     }
 }
        Returns:
        the comments text or Optional.empty() if there are no comments
        See Also:
        Protobuf plugin configuration
